OL,5,Cto school
OL,7,FA delay due to a pupil visiting the
OL,8,Fbakery chain, Greggs, known for its
OL,9,Fsausage rolls, was mentioned four
OL,10,Ftimes, with two of those specifically
OL,11,Freferencing Britain's favourite puff
OL,12,Fpastry snack.
OL,14,FOne child explained they were late
OL,15,Fbecause they "put blue food dye on a
OL,16,Fwaffle instead of syrup, and mum had
OL,17,Fto clean it off (their) face and hands
OL,18,Fbefore bringing (them) in."
