OL,7,FOthers said their Nan "took them to
OL,8,Fthe wrong school," and another claimed
OL,9,Fthey were late as they could not leave
OL,10,Ftheir home "until all toys had been
OL,11,Fhugged, because the toys have anxiety".
OL,13,FAnimals are a favourite excuse among
OL,14,Fstudents; encounters with squirrels,
OL,15,Fdead bats, and "looking at cows that
OL,16,Fweren't there" were among the reasons
OL,17,Fgiven for being late.
