OL,3,CGulls, Greggs and guinea fowl:
OL,4,CStudents' wild excuses for being late
OL,5,Cto school
OL,7,FThe Education Secretary Bridget
OL,8,FPhillipson, recently described the
OL,9,Fnumber of children missing school as
OL,10,Fan "absence epidemic", and warned the
OL,11,Fnumber has rocketed since the Covid-19
OL,12,Fpandemic.
OL,14,FA report by the Institute for Fiscal
OL,15,FStudies (IFS) published earlier this
OL,16,Fyear said nearly two in five (37%)
OL,17,Fpupils from disadvantaged backgrounds
OL,18,Fare "persistently absent", meaning
OL,19,Fthey miss at least one day of school
OL,20,Fper fortnight on average.
